title: [LFT] Looking for Ranked team / Bot lane partner to learn.

embed.description: turtle pace / Gold 2 19LP / 104W 104L Win Ratio 50% / Janna - 56W 41L Win Ratio 58%, Vayne - 17W 17L Win Ratio 50%, Anivia - 8W 3L Win Ratio 73%, Alistar - 3W 7L Win Ratio 30%, Jinx - 4W 5L Win Ratio 44%

body:
I am a support main that briefly sat in diamond SoloQ at the start of the season. Since then i went full time at work and  decayed down to gold. I now have more time to dedicate to the game.

I have decided that I no longer want to chase SoloQ as a goal and want to move into a more Team oriented playstyle. 
I currently sit at Gold II.
Age: 23
Can use TS, Discord, Skype
Have a stable internet connection
Currently don't have any commitments so can play and practice at any time.

I am looking for someone who plays ADC as a main or a team with players High gold up to Diamond to play with, but most importantly learn from and grow as a player.

If you feel you can offer me a position or believe I can offer something to your team reply to this or add me in game and send me a message.

replies.body:
Bump - Update

Still looking for a team.

currently sitting at plat 3 - hit me up if your looking for a support.
